I can't stand it.

00:50:11.900 --> 00:50:14.510
I feel like I'm this guy who's
70 years old, and you say,

00:50:14.510 --> 00:50:17.330
so what's your exit strategy?

00:50:17.330 --> 00:50:18.310
If I had to know?

00:50:18.310 --> 00:50:18.810
It's funny.

00:50:18.810 --> 00:50:20.820
So what would I
eat, my last meal?

